snippet.title: Master System Longplay [009] Captain Silver
snippet.description:
http://www.longplays.net

Played By: T-0815 

This is the Euro version!
The American version of the Master System port only contain four levels when its manual stated that it had more; also, the manual stated that there were more enemies and bosses than could actually be found in the game. These levels, enemies and bosses can be found in the Canadian and European versions. -
Disclaimer: Most videos by World of Longplays use SaveStates!
